code: import axios from'axios';var baseUrl='/api/workouts';var create=function create(newWorkout){var request=axios.post(baseUrl,newWorkout);return request.then(function(response){return response.data;});};var update=function update(id,newWorkout){var request=axios.put("{baseUrl}/".concat(id),newWorkout);return request.then(function(response){return response.data;});};export default{create:create,update:update};
